  "title": "Sales Support Administrator (Multiple Openings)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Attend to customers' sales order enquiries via calls and emails</p></li><li><p>Prepare sales quotations and confirm sales orders with clients</p></li><li><p>Perform sales order processing, coordinate delivery and ensure on-time delivery</p></li><li><p>Work closely with cross-functional team in fulfilling customers order promptly</p></li><li><p>Arrangement and coordination of transport, warehouse and delivery process</p></li><li><p>Contribute to the development of sales and customer service strategies</p></li><li><p>Proactively identify opportunities to improve processes and enhance the customer experience</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Ad hoc duties as assigned</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor or Diploma in Business Administration, Sales & Marketing, Supply Chain Management or equivalent</p></li><li><p>With 2 - 5 years of sales support or order processing experience</p></li><li><p>Candidate who is able to start work within short notice will be advantageous<br /></p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please send in your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:gs1@talenttradersg.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com</strong></a><br /></p><p>EA License No: 13C6305</p><p>Reg. No.: R24120209 (GAN CHYE SHEN)<br /></p><p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
